channel.title: OwnXile PK - It's Back by Robbie
channel.description:
[center][img]http://imgtool.us/images/bannerymy.png[/img]
OwnXile (previously PwnXile) is brought to you by Robbie.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/zKRtl0Q.png[/img]
[center][url=http://ownxile.com/index.php/page,play.html]Webclient[/url] | [url=http://ownxile.com/?page=dl]Download Client[/url] | [url=http://ownxile.com/index.php]Community Forums[/url] | [url=http://ownxile.com/index.php/page,vote.html]Vote for Rewards[/url] | [url=http://ownxile.com/index.php?page=hs]Hiscores[/url] [/center] Looking for an adventure? Start here! Welcome to OwnXile! We have plenty of active members who have come to OwnXile looking for a unique game with enjoyable content, all in which we offer.
Here at OwnXile we take a different approach the other generic servers you come across. We work endlessly to bring you a dedicated, high performance environment to play our enjoyable, content-filled server emulator.
We invest hundreds of dollars into our secure and stable server architecture to ensure dedicated uptime and a fast connection, all protected behind high quality firewall mechanisms. Security and stability are very important to us, that's why we make sure we are the best around at offering this.
The content that has been implemented into the server has created not only a massive community but it also has created a feature where every player can have the role to create their own content and add to the game. We take every approach to make sure that the content implemented is enjoyable and what every player wants.
Our Wilderness and intense minigames create challenges for those who seek more than just a game to play. Are you up for it? Come join OwnXile![/center]
